data.title: Florida International University (FIU) Library Digital Collection Repository System (dPanther)
data.meta_description: Florida International University (FIU) Library Digital Collection Repository System (dPanther) designed and developed by FIU GIS center / Digital Collection Center (DCC). Powered by dPanther web development Team
data.text: Record Accessed: 101 "Record Accessed" provides the total number which the item has been viewed through PURL page / url. These statistics directly indicates the usage of the selected item. Searched: 214 "Searched" provides the total number that the item has been concluded inside a search result. These statistics reflect the popularity of the selected item for end users.
